{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"443f5ebf3c","title":"大字报——反对便衣特务","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"469161e7b2","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"443f5ebf3c"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"5401b550ab","name":"魏盛余"},{"id":"8aff656cc4","name":"上海第一师范学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0ab2e6e298","type":"title","text":"大字报——反对便衣特务","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"443f5ebf3c"},{"id":"09149478da","type":"authors","text":"上海第一师范学院魏盛余","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"443f5ebf3c"},{"id":"bc5e31738f","type":"subtitle","text":"[魏盛余：中文科七班学生]","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"443f5ebf3c"},{"id":"6cc535bd02","type":"subtitle","text":"反对便衣特务","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"443f5ebf3c"},{"id":"8a9e7a6dcb","type":"paragraph","text":"有这样一种人，年龄较大经验丰富，当看你面嘻嘻哈哈，或者一言不发，从来不向你提半个批评，半点意见。但在背后却用日记写下了你的一言一行，和你从来不曾注意过的戏谑语。一点也不漏，甚至记下了何时何地，何人在场跟何人讲的，仿佛象交代个人历史似的，以记确凿而又如此详尽。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"443f5ebf3c"},{"id":"38e8018193","type":"paragraph","text":"后来他就带着历史典籍似的“情报日记本”在组织面前极尽其想象能力，把问题提到原则的最高度上去作高瞻远眺的汇报，爱说爱笑争论的同学就此打下了18层地狱，戴上了各式各样的“莫须有”的帽子。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"443f5ebf3c"},{"id":"474213741d","type":"paragraph","text":"这类人中某些同志在宿舍里，原来大家认为他是和蔼可亲的，继而怀疑失望，再则，敬鬼神而远之，以免“病从口入”使得一个朝气蓬勃的宿舍穿上了死气沉沉的外衣。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"443f5ebf3c"},{"id":"510b2a9374","type":"paragraph","text":"在“鸣放”中，我们不怕党委，而最怕他们，只要他们一记上帐我们就有冤也无处伸。反对了这种人，我们的胆子就会大起来，据知这种人为数不少。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"443f5ebf3c"},{"id":"778bb05770","type":"paragraph","text":"不知党委怎样对待这种人，我们的态度是反对20世纪50年代的“薛宝钗”。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"443f5ebf3c"},{"id":"0bc9884aca","type":"paragraph","text":"请求党委支持我们","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"443f5ebf3c"},{"id":"c9b262e0a9","type":"paragraph","text":"为避记仇，恕不具名。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"443f5ebf3c"},{"id":"2abaa2f498","type":"paragraph","text":" —群同学（系中文科七班魏盛余冒群众名义写的）","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"443f5ebf3c"},{"id":"0cbbaa58b6","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《鸣放言论选集》（上海第一师范学院，1957）","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"443f5ebf3c"}],"page":{"id":"db73ca326c","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"443f5ebf3c","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}